Formerly a market exchange where bitcoins were bought and sold.  Funds were deposited by mailing in cash.  When funds were withdrawn cash was mailed to the customer.

Bitcoin2cash, LLC is an entity registered in the State of Alabama (1.1).

##History

The site was originally announced on July 13th, 2010 (2.1). The site was subsequently redesigned and the new availability was announced on April 2nd, 2011 (2.2).  Sometime before April 18th, 2012 the operator suspended service. 

